<GuideLayout
  title="HRA and Rent Receipt Guide for India | JaldiDocs"
  description="Understand basic HRA exemption inputs, rent receipts, landlord PAN and document checks before submitting proofs to your employer."
  canonical="/guides/hra-rent-receipt-guide/"
>
  <article class="prose-tool space-y-7">
    <h1>HRA and Rent Receipt Guide</h1>
    <p>
      Salaried employees who receive House Rent Allowance may need rent receipts and rent details for
      employer proof submission. Requirements can vary by employer and current tax rules.
    </p>
    <h2>Common details needed</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Tenant and landlord name</li>
      <li>Rented address and rent amount</li>
      <li>Payment month and receipt number</li>
      <li>Landlord signature</li>
      <li>Landlord PAN when annual rent crosses applicable limits</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Use the <a href="/tools/hra-calculator/">HRA Calculator</a> for a quick estimate and the
      <a href="/tools/rent-receipt-generator/">Rent Receipt Generator</a> to create clean monthly receipts.
    </p>
  </article>
</GuideLayout>
